amily:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\"></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323111921_80135.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"200\" /><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\" class=\"15\">总侧向一边睡觉。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">这样会对被压一侧的头骨形成压力，导致骨头间产生细小错位。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\" class=\"15\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#000000;\">托下巴。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">很多人看书、上网时喜欢一手托着下巴，这样会对面颊和下巴施加压力，导致变形。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\"></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323111854_19654.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"200\" /><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">　　<span style=\"color:#000000;\">用一侧嚼东西。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">这样会导致单侧面颊肌肉的发达。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">　　用嘴呼吸。用嘴呼吸的一大弊端是令嘴角的肌肉松弛，进而破坏脸部肌肉平衡。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:21pt;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">&nbsp;如果发现脸颊两侧明显不对称，通过以下措施可以改善：1.按摩脸颊两侧颧骨下缘的凹陷处，同时张大嘴发“啊、咦、呜、哎、哦”音。2.闭上嘴，舌头沿上下牙龈画圈，早晚各做数十遍。　</span> \r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:#f7fcff;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"> \r\n		<p>\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"> \r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span></span> \r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;background:#f7fcff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;backg