:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#000000;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>和兴白花油</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323144946_63382.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"251\" /><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">第一样当然跟旅行有关，不管是舟车晕浪、头晕头痛都可以舒缓的，容易晕车的朋友，出门在外必备白花油，</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">既可以舒缓初起伤风感冒引起之鼻塞、舒缓肌肉疼痛</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">小朋友被蚊虫咬伤</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">只要用两三滴白花油涂擦患处即可消炎，凉凉的舒服</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">白花油是香港出产的名牌</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">有八十年历丈史</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">质量有保证</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">推荐大家备用</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>2</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>黄道益活络油</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145006_68773.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"261\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">接着是爱好运动者和同年长人士都能用到的黄道益活络油，它具备趺打肿痛、腰酸背痛、舒筋活络功效，只需搽上</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">2-3</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">滴，</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">按</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">15-20</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">分钟、力度由轻至重</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">便可以舒缓不适。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">黄道益活络油己有</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">47</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">年历史</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">是全球老少患者最爱的药品之一，现时每人只限购</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">2</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">份</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>3</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>胃仙</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>U</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145024_46223.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"185\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">老公经常在外应酬</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">吃得很少又油腻、光喝酒搞到肠胃不适，给他买了胃药试试，买的是很有名的胃仙</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">U,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">想不到效果不错</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">老公吃了药以后说感觉好多了</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">它可以调节胃肠机能</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">节制胃液过度分泌</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">中和胃酸及消除胃痛、胃胀</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">使胃肠机能正常，胃仙</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">U</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">当之无愧为每个家庭必备的常用良药之一</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>4</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>日本人字牌救心丸</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145057_23346.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"288\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">我的朋友一直以来心脏都不好</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">血压及心跳不稳定，又易晕心绞痛出冷汗，需要准备救心药以防不时之需，自从我介绍他服食人字牌救心丸</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">心绞痛时使用效果神奇，很快便平伏下来。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">虽然价钱略高</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">但是相比大药厂的昂贵心脏药价钱还是便宜，日本用的都是最好的药材，我真心推荐不同年龄患者试一试</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">记得香港购买</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">有个遇热变红的封口贴才是正品。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>5</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>京都念慈庵蜜炼川贝枇杷膏</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145123_37013.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"288\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">经常容易患有伤风感冒的朋友气管较虚及敏感，天气变或休息不够会易咳，川贝枇杷膏为这些朋友的一种常备</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:underline;\">的</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">药品。此药品属性平和</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">不寒不燥</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">男女老幼都可以食。对于痰稠、痰多气喘、咽喉干痒效果不错。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">职业性用声的朋友如教师和唱歌爱好者，声音嘶哑时使用有想不到的效果</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>6</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>林淦生R</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>鼻敏清</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145321_99960.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"288\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">中国受空气污染及气温变化不常的影响下人人都鼻敏感。鼻炎发作，买纸巾都买了不少钱，还被人误会感冒个个敬而远之，很尴尬。前年朋友介绍我用林淦生</span><span><img src=\"file://C:/DOCUME~1/ADMINI~1/LOCALS~1/Temp/ksohtml/wps50D.tmp.jpg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">鼻敏清，用了两三支真的很好，現在回到广州发作少了，病情都轻了很多</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">鼻敏感药物五花八门，但真正解决到问题的很难找</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">林淦生</span><span><img src=\"file://C:/DOCUME~1/ADMINI~1/LOCALS~1/Temp/ksohtml/wps50E.tmp.jpg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">鼻敏清是香港品牌当地制造，牌子有</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">30</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">年历史，价钱贵但省了其它鼻药和纸巾钱</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">香港各区的华润堂、万宁等均有售，药房有好多都叫鼻敏清的药，但一定要认准林淦生牌子及有中药注册的才是正货</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>7</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>必妥碘</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>&nbsp;(&nbsp;BETADINE)&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>冰凉消毒漱口水</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145350_25170.png\" width=\"288\" height=\"195\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">这支田蕊妮代言既漱口水可以消除痱滋、喉部感染发炎之征状及伤风感冒引起之喉咙痛，对于感冒前喉咙痕和流鼻涕的朋友很有用</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">本来用于于牙科手术期间及之后</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">作为预防性消毒剂，但普通人也可以自己用，大概是</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">1:2</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">用清水稀释，漱口</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">1</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">分钟至漱口水由浊变清即可，大概</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">80</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">多港币一支。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">欧洲制造的必妥碘冰凉消毒漱口水系现代感冒这样普片的生活环境之家居必不可少品。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>8</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>姑嫂丸、天喜丸</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145416_54262.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145437_27284.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">2</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">样都是四物汤的基本上改变而来。调经姑嫂丸重补血，但偏温偏燥，适用于气血虚实寒。天喜丸补气养血，能寒热并用主治妇女月经失调及因而引至的各种妇科问题，适用于月经不正常、白带、经痛等。无论是己婚或是未婚，均可进服。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">如果是怕冷明显的，则用姑嫂丸；气血虚，明显腰酸腿软，心烦，口渴的可以服天喜丸。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>9</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>新一代液体胶布</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:277px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145511_71158.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"360\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">家中煮饭打理家务，加上近来天气干燥，灼伤、烫伤、割伤、龟裂等等在所难免，我一定推介新一代液体胶布</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">适用于保护割伤、擦伤、灼伤及手术后缝合伤口等。迅速干透凝固﹐有特强持久黏贴力﹐可紧贴如肤，可避免因煮食</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">､</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">清洗等活动﹐伤口被水分渗入或异物磨擦而产生痛楚，非常透气﹐不会阻碍皮肤呼吸及散热</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">｡</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">一般在清理伤口后</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">用笔式搽毛涂搽适量在患处﹐然后让其自然风干</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">｡&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">若要较厚保护膜</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">数分钟后再涂搽一次。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">它具有防水、防菌、透气、弹性、美观功能等五大优点。我推荐它给天下的母亲</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>第</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>10</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>种</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>双飞人药水</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323145532_93676.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"172\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">香港人普遍用一种药水以治屙呕肚痛、烫火灼伤、伤风感冒、牙痛头痛、驱风救急</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">功效卓著。历史上可追溯到</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:PMingLiU;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">20</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">世纪法国人殖民安南、金边、辽国等地，当时这药水用途广泛，军用民用都赞不绝口，因此现当地华侨多携带此药水以馈赠亲友，可见此药水之如何受人珍视。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\">法国双飞人药水为著名老牌良药，已畅销世界各地厉百余年之久。在香港药房买的时候要留心是否正货，贪小便宜买下假的就不好了。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427065636', '', '0', 'http://', '', '9213', '0', '551');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`, `click_count`, `rel_clickcount`, `love` ) VALUES  ('63', '18', '五招教你快速去除粉刺的小窍门', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0px;color:#000000;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_0__\"></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/NPv8Ib9HvuIYJ7ygEhEAhRpcRQlxsEMlo9k5M7JWepianJicv22GaBDyBUHNwWoV1IPWibfiboZvAXCl9qC2bkIRiaA/0\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></strong></span><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	 提醒:点击标题下方的“</span><span><span style=\"color:#0070c0;\">实实商城</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">”即可免费订阅我，随时发现，采集，分享你喜欢的一切。</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	如果你的粉刺是</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">黑头的，这多半与你过度的户外奔波有关，白头粉刺与你在焦虑状况下大幅度进食甜食和高热量食品有关，无头粉刺通常是神经高度紧张的结果。下面</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">小编为大家</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">分享快速去粉刺小窍门有哪些，五招有效去除粉刺，快来看看吧。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:296px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323154507_91817.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"338\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#ee33ee;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\">第一：阿斯匹林</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">所含的水杨酸，具有去角质</span><span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">并且清洁毛孔的功能，是对抗粉刺的利器之一，因此可以运用阿斯匹林自制面膜，敷在有粉刺困扰的区域以达到清除粉刺的功效。你只需要将五到七颗的阿斯匹林压碎，并加入一茶匙的蜂蜜</span><span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">均匀搅拌即可制成。但对阿斯匹林过敏的患者请跳过这个方法啰!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323154747_35802.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"217\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#ee33ee;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\">第二：牛奶</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">牛奶是家中的必需品，因此非常容易取得。而牛奶也是对于改善皮肤非常好的食物。将一杯半小茶杯的红糖加入三茶匙的牛奶以及一茶匙蜂蜜，混和完成后以去角质方式搓揉肌肤，可以达到去除老废角质以及调整肌肤的功效。牛奶中的脂肪可以柔嫩你的肌肤，而乳酸则能温和的代谢阻塞毛孔的老废角质。但若你是油性的肌肤，则用量上要减少一些。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323154813_26308.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"287\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#ee33ee;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\">第三：燕麦</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">燕麦有天然的去角质和镇定肌肤的特性，而它的收敛功能也能清洁并柔嫩肌肤。用四分之三杯的原味燕麦(不建议使用加味的燕麦)，加入一杯水后快煮一至两分钟，放凉后即可作为面膜使用，建议使用10到20分钟即可洗掉。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323154955_70911.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"276\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#ee33ee;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\">第四：牙膏</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">对于老一倍的妈妈们来说，牙膏是去除粉刺的好东西，而他们所含有的硫化物也确实对去除粉刺有帮助。但是请避开有美白功效以及标榜除垢功能的牙膏，因为那将会造成肌肤红肿发炎的可能，尤其过敏性肌肤更是特别要避免。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323155710_70414.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"268\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#ee33ee;font-size:24px;font-weight:normal;\">第五：抗炎止痛药─布洛芬</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">胶状的布洛芬对于将要并发的青春痘十分有效，因为它在抗红肿和消炎镇定有非常显著的效果。你只需要简单的将胶囊打开并且将里面的胶状物涂抹于患处即可。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427068753', '', '0', 'http://', '', '5275', '0', '332');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`, `click_count`, `rel_clickcount`, `love` ) VALUES  ('64', '21', '主题婚礼现场布置 让婚礼美不胜收', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0px;color:#000000;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_0__\"></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/NPv8Ib9HvuIYJ7ygEhEAhRpcRQlxsEMlo9k5M7JWepianJicv22GaBDyBUHNwWoV1IPWibfiboZvAXCl9qC2bkIRiaA/0\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></strong></span><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	 提醒:点击标题下方的“</span><span><span style=\"color:#0070c0;\">实实商城</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">”即可免费订阅我，随时发现，采集，分享你喜欢的一切。</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	今天为大家带来的是不同主题婚礼现场布置</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\" class=\"16\">效果图</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">，让你的婚礼美不胜收。一点小细节就能让画龙点睛，可千万不要让小地方拖了你婚礼的后腿哦~下面快随小编一起来看看吧</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323161858_44933.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"212\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;\">老上海复古婚礼</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\">有一种空间，它低调、奢华，骨子里透露出浓浓的文人趣味。有一种气质，它自由、开放，处处显露着海纳百川的胸怀。这就是老上海的精神，在怀旧风盛行的今天，它被定义成一种风格，代表了经典与复古。二三十年代的旧上海，那是个传奇而又富有神秘色彩的年代，愿他们的爱情也同那个时代一般，纵然经过时间的冲刷也不褪色。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323162200_84584.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"190\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">波西米亚风格主题婚礼</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\">绚丽的色彩，引人瞩目的视觉效果，这是很多新人追求的梦中婚礼。如果你就是其中一员，那么这样的绚丽波西米亚主题婚礼一定会是你的菜!新娘的胸花，新娘的花环以及手捧花、项链都融入了色彩斑斓的波西米亚风元素。看着这样一场色彩的视觉盛宴，谁会不爱呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323162222_57858.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"192\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;\">户外草坪主题婚礼</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\">这一抹明黄，似遇见可可西里的清澈，又似莫妮卡妖娆眼神的即视感，在醒目而舒适的色彩里顾盼生辉，这才不辜负这个百花争先恐后开放的热情，它温暖纯粹给人所有美好的想象空间，唤醒所有感官尽情的去享受吧。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323162248_11882.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"216\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">绕滚风格主题婚礼</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\">一场摇滚重金属风格的婚礼。上面是灰色的水泥墙为婚礼背景，钢筋水管为装饰元素。两人在婚礼上选择演唱的歌曲，左右乐队、逃跑计划......</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323162507_61822.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"192\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;\">爱丽丝梦游仙境主题婚礼</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\">如果不想走出去，那就让森林走到室内来，于百花齐放，万兽共鸣中奏响一场森林狂欢派对的序曲，在亦幻亦真的爱丽丝仙境中开启一段奇幻之旅。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"><img style=\"width:288px;height:302px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323162744_31048.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"434\" /><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#4c33e5;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#cc33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;\">孔雀主题婚礼</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\">婚礼场地足够精致，为保万无一失，是不是该仔细检查检查有什么忽略了?椅背装饰怎么能这么粗心大意，不做任何装点呢?千篇一律怎么会是80、90新人们的风格，创意才是他们的新主张，看看这21种椅背装饰是否给你的婚礼一定启发?&nbsp;孔雀主题婚礼不可缺少的一部分</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427070619', '', '0', 'http://', '', '6941', '1', '598');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`, `click_count`, `rel_clickcount`, `love` ) VALUES  ('65', '14', '想要容易受孕双胞胎 揭秘生双胞胎诀窍', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0px;color:#000000;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_0__\"></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/NPv8Ib9HvuIYJ7ygEhEAhRpcRQlxsEMlo9k5M7JWepianJicv22GaBDyBUHNwWoV1IPWibfiboZvAXCl9qC2bkIRiaA/0\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></strong></span><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	 提醒:点击标题下方的“</span><span><span style=\"color:#0070c0;\">实实商城</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">”即可免费订阅我，随时发现，采集，分享你喜欢的一切。</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	想知道生双胞胎有什么秘诀吗?看着别人家的双胞胎宝宝是不是都很羡慕呢?现在，就让小编来告诉</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\" class=\"15\">你怎样容易受孕双胞胎</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323175706_98052.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"216\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ee33ee;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4c33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>1.具有双胞胎基因的妈妈生双胞胎的几率大</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">能否怀上双胞胎遗传的基因主要是在母亲这边，也就是说如果母亲是双胞胎，那么再次生下双胞胎几率就高达1.7%。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ee33ee;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4c33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>2.吃中草药容易怀孕生双胞胎</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">有些医治不孕症的中药孕育发生双胞胎的机率比较大，但是要注意的是使用这个方法，应提前咨询医生哪些类型的不孕症中药对怀双胞胎有促进作用，确定这些药会不会对身体造成不良影响。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323175816_98086.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"314\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ee33ee;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4c33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>3.利用试管婴儿增加怀双胞胎几率</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">通常在进行试管婴儿时，为了保证受精卵的质量，一般会多选几个卵受精。有些女性的身体条件允许两个胚胎同时发育，自己又想生双胞胎，就可以让医生为其保留两个胚胎，孕育一对双胞胎宝宝。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ee33ee;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4c33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>4.孕前服用叶酸增加排卵</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">瑞典一医学研究机构研究指出，服用叶酸的女性怀双胞胎的机会比没有服用的女性高出近一倍。专家估计，叶酸补充剂可能会增加排卵的次数，使多个卵子进入子宫，从而产生双胞胎。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150323/20150323175903_98514.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"217\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ee33ee;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4c33e5;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>5.在7月份受孕</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">在7月份卵子受精而育成双胞胎的机遇，比其他月份要高。因此，7月受孕更容易怀孕生双胞胎。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ee33ee;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4c33e5;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>6.服用促排卵药物</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">服用排卵药物可以促进卵泡发育，增加排卵量，增加受孕几率，同时也能提高怀双胎的概率。但是服用促排卵药物会对女性的身体带来一定的伤害，所以在使用此方法时要慎重。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ee33ee;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4c33e5;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\"><strong>7.多吃番薯有助于生双胞胎</strong></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#cccccc;font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">番薯含有一种与雌激素类似的精神，有助于生养孩子。有研究称尼日利亚的约鲁巴族妇女多吃番薯，而此族人生双胞胎的几率是全球最高的。因此若想怀孕生双胞胎可以尝试下。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427077020', '', '0', 'http://', '', '5643', '0', '391');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`, `click_count`, `rel_clickcount`, `love` ) VALUES  ('66', '18', '护肤达人告诉你什么才是无添加化妆品', '<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0px;color:#000000;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_0__\"></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/NPv8Ib9HvuIYJ7ygEhEAhRpcRQlxsEMlo9k5M7JWepianJicv22GaBDyBUHNwWoV1IPWibfiboZvAXCl9qC2bkIRiaA/0\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></strong></span><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	 提醒:点击标题下方的“</span><span><span style=\"color:#0070c0;\">实实商城</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">”即可免费订阅我，随时发现，采集，分享你喜欢的一切。</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\" align=\"center\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150330/20150330165442_34251.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"194\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">目前在国内，“无添加”可说是红透了半边天。纵观各大坛子，评价“无添加”的，要求代购“无添加”的，比比皆是。“无添加”乍一听上去，真的很有诱惑力。植物、天然、无刺激、无副作用，“无添加”成了它们的代名词。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">可是，当你选择“无添加”的时候，你是否认真的考虑过，“无添加”的真正内涵是什么？都有哪些东西没有被添加？为什么没有被添加？没有了这些物质的添加，化妆品是否还能起到应有的作用？</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">作为20年护肤经验，接触过市面80%的化妆品的小达人，今天就来告诉你什么才是真正的无添加！</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">首先，先和大家科普一下“无添加”的知识，所谓无添加化妆品，是指以有机植物为主要原料，不添加人工香料、人工色素、不含石油成份，所添加的防腐剂及表面活性剂必须受到严格限制，且制造过程需符合相关规定，不能使用动物实验及利用放射线杀菌的产品。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">此外，做到不添加化学产品之外，更为重要的一点是有无添加肤品的原料要求在培养、生产、萃取、制作的环境（如土壤）及过程中，不受基因变种及人工化学添加剂的影响。也就是说，“无添加”化妆品的重点在原材料上。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">接着再来说说原材料，无机的最差，也就是添加化学成分的化妆品，然后是有机，但是</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">大部分人</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">不让说有机化妆品，所以说是无添加。简而言之，无添加就是不添加任何的化学成分的有机材料化妆品，各位get到了吗？</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">但有机里面也有好坏区分，是有的原材料就是很差的，比如用的是国产的有机，或者更加没良心的直接从化学产品中提炼成分，这种东西用到脸上，后果可想而知。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">原材料中最好的就是活机，活机与有机最大的差距就是活机用的都是全世界最好的原材料，比如大马士革玫瑰</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">、</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">南美洲安第斯山脉蔷薇，</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">小编</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">目前在用的一款化妆品，叫莫施，他家的产品就都是活机材料，比如有很多含有苹果酸的化妆品，一些商家的苹果都来自国内，而莫施用的是日本富士山的苹果，楼主用的莫施橄榄精华油，用的就是西班牙幼嫩橄榄，整个油都是白色的，其他产品么，用的都是老橄榄，买来一看，油都黄了。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">说道这里，想必大家心里都有数了，所谓“无添加”的化妆品，是需要很多科学技术支持的，包括这些材料的保质啊什么的，过期了的你敢用？</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">当然，朋友圈和某宝泛滥的什么自家手工“无添加”化妆品的好坏，也就不用</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">小编</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#4a4a4a;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">再多说了吧！</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:14pt;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427133318', '', '0', 'http://', '', '6845', '0', '345');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`, `click_count`, `rel_clickcount`, `love` ) VALUES  ('67', '18', '2015新娘美甲 小细节成就完美婚礼', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0px;color:#000000;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_0__\"></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/NPv8Ib9HvuIYJ7ygEhEAhRpcRQlxsEMlo9k5M7JWepianJicv22GaBDyBUHNwWoV1IPWibfiboZvAXCl9qC2bkIRiaA/0\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></strong></span><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	 提醒:点击标题下方的“</span><span><span style=\"color:#0070c0;\">实实商城</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">”即可免费订阅我，随时发现，采集，分享你喜欢的一切。</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	在新娘造型中，美甲绝对</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">是非常重要的一环，当你伸出双手戴上戒指的一刹那，众人的目光都会聚焦在你的双手，如果只是一款平淡无奇的法式美甲，未免也太没有新意了。小编为大家带来了10款2015最新的新娘美甲</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">图片，快来看看吧</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\">!!</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:345px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324101154_71002.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"431\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">以肉色甲油做底，再加上水钻装饰的美甲会显得非常华丽浪漫，不过要是每个手指都如此也有点过于沉闷，所以不如给你戴上钻戒的无名指加点蕾丝装饰，既出彩又能跟其他的美甲有所区别</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:357px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324101231_64936.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"434\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">金属装饰的美甲比普通的彩绘美甲更显妖娆妩媚，所以一定不能在所有指甲上都使用这种方法，同样选择无名指来做区别，就会很好看。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:346px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324101327_97146.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"431\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">纯白色的美甲会容易显手黑，不过加入一些银色线条做装饰，会有提亮的效果。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:380px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324101900_70983.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"436\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">有创意的新娘就不会只甘于做肉色美甲，像这款就是用深蓝色做底，再用一些简单的线条描绘出心形，虽然简单但是很有个性。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:374px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324102043_35419.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"424\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">半圆式描边的画法今年非常流行，你也可以尝试看看，并且使用金色、银色这种亮眼的颜色进行描边，效果会抢眼。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img style=\"width:288px;height:384px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324102343_67872.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"431\" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">蕾丝图案一直以来都很受欢迎，你可以选择浅色甲油做底，创作温柔可人的美甲，也可以使用深色甲油做底，让整体效果更酷。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:404px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324102447_85060.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"428\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">藕粉色并不是热门的新娘美甲色，不过它会让手显得更加白皙粉嫩，其实很值得一试。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:387px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324102821_56411.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"433\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">浪漫的波点图案很有小女人气质，看惯了法式美甲，你也可以试试这款。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:374px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324102922_53984.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"431\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">以肉色美甲做底，用金色线条来进行装饰的美甲造型</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">非常酷，会跟你浪漫的婚纱</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">形成极大差。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:288px;height:345px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150324/20150324102956_60280.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"434\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\">谁说狂野的豹纹图案不能应用在新娘美甲中，重点是只能在一个指甲上画，让你变身性感新娘。要是满手都画上豹纹图案，就未免狂野过头了</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:13pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427135461', '', '0', 'http://', '', '4791', '0', '59');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`, `click_count`, `rel_clickcount`, `love` ) VALUES  ('68', '17', '小明滚出去 第一季', '<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0px;color:#000000;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_0__\"></span><span style=\"color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/NPv8Ib9HvuIYJ7ygEhEAhRpcRQlxsEMlo9k5M7JWepianJicv22GaBDyBUHNwWoV1IPWibfiboZvAXCl9qC2bkIRiaA/0\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></strong></span><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	 提醒:点击标题下方的“</span><span><span style=\"color:#0070c0;\">实实商城</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">”即可免费订阅我，随时发现，采集，分享你喜欢的一切。</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></strong></span></span></span></strong> \r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150330/20150330165129_83230.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"288\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">1、老师问：世界上有一种马，由黑白颜色组成，请问是什么马？</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">小明：二维码！</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：滚出去</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:12pt;?=\"\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">2、音乐课上，老师问：“同学们都喜欢什么音乐呀？”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">小明大声道：“老师，下课铃声算不算音乐啊？”&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：“也算吧！”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">小明：“我喜欢。”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：“滚出去。”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:12pt;?=\"\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">3、老师：你一天就知道看小说，不好好学习，也没见你写部小说。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">小明：你每天都拉翔，也没见你吃。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：滾。。。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:12pt;?=\"\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">4、小明：老师，从1到－1的距离一定是2吗？</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：一定是啊，1减－1等于2，这是真理，不会错的。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">小明：那为什么楼层从1层到－1层的距离只有1层？</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：给我滚出去。。。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:12pt;?=\"\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">5、今天，老师发测试卷，老师说：“&nbsp;难的可以不用写。”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师刚要发给小明，小明却说：“老师您可以不用发给我了。”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师说：“为什么。”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">“您不是说男的可以不用写吗？”&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：滚出去。。。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:12pt;?=\"\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">6、老师：“谁能给大家讲个故事，小明你来讲个吧。”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">小明：“就讲个我爸妈的事吧。星期一我爸做了道菜，妈说不好吃，爸甩了妈一巴掌：我做饭还是你做饭！星期二我爸买了个窗帘，妈说颜色不好看，爸甩了妈一巴掌：我买还是你买！星期四我爸。。。”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：“星期三还没说呢？”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">小明甩了老师一巴掌：“我讲故事还是你讲故事！”</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">老师：“滚出去！”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:12pt;?=\"\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">7、小明去浴池洗澡，看到老师也在里面洗，就想过去和老师打招呼。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;background:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:no