gb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span></span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(217,150,148); COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">一、敷完面膜要不要洗？</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">这是问的最多的问题了！</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">其实没有硬性规定，敷完面膜要不要洗~&nbsp;而且面膜的种类有很多种，就给大家大致的说一下~~</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(217,150,148)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">1.贴片式面膜</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">最简单方便的面膜，也是最多人喜欢用的。一张面膜的精华液基本在25~35ml左右，敷个15分钟左右拿下来，脸上会剩些精华液，轻轻按摩一会儿，让精华液更好的被肌肤所吸收。</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">这时候重点来了！如果你觉得按摩后脸上还是黏黏的，精华液多，那可以用清水冲洗一下，然后进行后续的护肤步骤；如果按摩后觉得精华吸收的差不多了，也没有粘腻的感觉，那其实可以不用再次洗脸的，直接进行后面的护肤步骤即可！</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(217,150,148)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">2.凝胶/果冻面膜</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">这种就是普通的水洗面膜了，敷个15~20分钟，用清水冲洗或者搭配海绵洗掉，会感觉皮肤水水嫩嫩的；也有很多人会把这个跟贴片式面膜一起搭配，做“三明治面膜”，这个看个人喜欢吧，我自己感觉“三明治面膜”也没有多么神奇的效果……</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(217,150,148)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">3.睡眠面膜</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">很多睡眠面膜都写着免洗，这个顾名思义，就是可以敷着睡觉的面膜。如果你要敷着过夜，薄薄的一层就可以了，太厚重反而会导致肌肤没办法正常代谢呼吸，而且容易蹭到被子枕头上。第二天起床后，一定要用洗面奶认认真真的洗个脸！</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(217,150,148)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">4.撕拉面膜</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">有些清洁面膜就是撕拉型的，尤其是一些去黑头的鼻膜，揭下后看到上面密密麻麻的感觉心里很爽有木有？但是很多人揭下后就开始正常护肤步骤了，完全忽略了要收敛毛孔这一步，导致几天后黑头卷土重来。。。。不管是撕拉鼻膜还是面膜，揭下后，一定要用清水冲洗一遍，然后用收敛水湿敷一会儿，帮助收缩毛孔。</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(217,150,148); COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">二、敷面膜前要先护肤吗？</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">我们一般都习惯洗好脸直接敷面膜，其实这完全可以的。不过，你也可以在敷面膜前，先上一层爽肤水或者肌底液或者保湿精华，再敷面膜，效果会更好哦！</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(217,150,148); COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">三、睡眠面膜真的可以过夜吗？</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">睡眠面膜当然可以过夜，不然为什么叫睡眠面膜？不过，睡眠面膜不可以天天敷，一个星期3次左右差不多了，不然到时候满脸闭口粉刺就是自找的咯！</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(217,150,148); COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=15 helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;?=\"\">四、面膜要从下往上揭吗？</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;background:#ffffff;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\">为了对抗地心引力，不让自己的脸下垂，建议你敷完面膜后从下往上揭咯~（特别是用撕拉面膜的妹子）</span><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\" helvetica=\"\" neue?;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;?=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \" new=\"\" times=\"\" roman?;font-size:10.5pt;?=\"\"></span>\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427159770', '', '0', 'http://', '', '6801', '0', '549');
