upload/image/20150325/20150325112913_69947.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"189\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">1.窗外下起了倾盆大雨，独自在家的你会做什么呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">站在窗旁看落雨→2</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">倾听雨点敲击屋檐的声音→4</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">继续做自己的事情→5</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">2.你在精品店看上了一个很喜欢的东西，但是价格超出了你的预算，你该怎么办?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">试着跟老板砍价→5</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">恋恋不舍地离开→3</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">回家取钱买下→6</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">3.你会轻易改变</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">自己的发型</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">吗?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">不是→5</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">是的→6</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">偶尔改变→4</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">4.假如你错过了最后一班回家的公车，你该怎么办?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">坐出租车回去→6</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">让人来接自己→7</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">自己步行回去→8</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">5.你觉得什么颜色最能代表“忧郁”?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">黑色→7</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">紫色→4</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">蓝色→8</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">6.你喜欢低沉而略带忧郁的女声吗?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">是的，听起来很舒服→8</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">什么样的声音都能接受→9</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">7.假如你要进入歌坛当一名歌手，你会选择什么路线呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">创作型歌手→9</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">偶像歌手→10</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">实力派歌手→8</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">8.你相信塔罗牌</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">算命</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">吗?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">相信→11</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">不相信→10</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">将信将疑→9</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">9.你和朋友一起去到了游乐园，你们会选择游玩什么呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">旋转木马→12</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">鬼屋探险→11</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">过山车→10</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">10.你和朋友约定好在购物中心见面，但是他迟到了，你会怎样打发时间呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">看购物中心附近的大幅广告→11</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">看着身边来来往往的行人→12</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">拿出手机玩→13</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150325/20150325113117_58061.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"197\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">11.你最喜欢的包包的形状是哪种呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">方形→15</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">圆形→12</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">其他形状→14</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">12.你比较喜欢下列哪种质地的布料?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">呢子→14</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">真丝→15</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">帆布→13</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">13.夏日炎炎，你想自己动手做沙冰，那你会选择什么口味的呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">西瓜沙冰→F</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">柠檬沙冰→B</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">苹果沙冰→15</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">14.你比较喜欢下面哪种蛋糕</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">黑森林蛋糕→A</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">抹茶蛋糕→D</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">布丁蛋糕→F</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">15.图上画了一片一望无垠的海面，你会在上面添加什么呢?</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">一轮太阳→14</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">几只海鸟→E</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">一只小船→C</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150325/20150325113226_54267.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"190\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#003399;font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;\">测试结果</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">A.曾经爱的人</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">有一种感情，越是得不到才越完美。你常常会在夜里怀念起那段的爱情和那个熟悉的身影，想想TA现在过得还好不好。怀旧的你偶尔会想起从前那些甜蜜的时光，当记忆落下帷幕，你就会禁不住对这段曾经缱绻悱恻的感情产生淡淡的忧伤。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">B.金钱</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">你是一个患得患失的人，有时候想到借出去没讨回的钱或者是不应该花掉的钱，你就会有一阵心痛的感觉，懊悔万分，埋怨自己当时怎么那么不清醒。金钱至上是你的一个宗旨，假如你一下失去一大笔金钱，会是令你很痛心的事情。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/image/20150325/20150325113316_22820.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"172\" /><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">C.朋友</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">你是一个依赖心很重的人，假如没人陪你就会觉得一个人很凄凉，很心酸，所以你离不开朋友的陪伴。但是，有时候因为口角或误会，某个朋友与你渐行渐远，你就会很难过，希望这个错误没发生过，希望你们还能像以前一样形影不离。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">D.家人</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">你是一个很重感情的人，你非常舍不得扔掉每一样旧东西，你的脑子里充满了故事与回忆。打开记忆的抽屉，你就会情不自禁地想到已经离开的家人，回忆起曾经温暖的时光，相比起现在的形单影只。</span><span><a href=\"http://www.wed114.cn/jiehun/hunjiaqinggan/jiatingshenghuo/\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"15\">家庭</span></a></span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">的力量是你最大的支柱，假如可以挽回，你一定会对家人说“我爱你”。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">E.梦想</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">你是一个充满幻想和浪漫忧伤的人，你心里有着自己年少时单纯而快乐的梦想，但是时光像一趟列车呼啸前行，从前的梦想开始变得不切实际，生活变得让人疲惫，那些梦想已经开始黯淡失色，看着自己的梦想仿佛泡沫般消失，心里难免会有说不出的怅惘。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#e53333;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">F.童年</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:0pt;\" class=\"p\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#337fe5;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\">童年仿佛一块涂满五颜六色的色彩的调色板，各种滋味尽在其中。偶尔在泛黄的杂物堆里找到童年的气息和痕迹，回忆之匣就会打开，有一种感动油然而生，童年时的玩具，童年时的亲人，童年时的老街道，一切都是那么亲切，但是一切都不再复返，想到这里你就会对童年无限的怀恋。</span><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span> \r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427225643', '', '0', 'http://', '', '9862', '0', '763');
