l, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">——“直到一年之后，我才慢慢找出摸索着画画的方法。”</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4SV0KPgHFrLibPyoP7Pps1RrKJeccpRvufX7v5uDPdvAYYU5Iia5XPFlA/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">——“基本上，我就是把普通画家用眼睛做的事情全部换成了用手。”</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4tCUbQYO6C4SJrXeYRDiauBJDJkN4Yb3DFxfBELjic3E69Yucbl1RiastQ/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">——“如果你仔细想想，就会发现在画画时，眼睛其实只做了两件事：定位和选色。”</span><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4pV8IUUUDeEtmQ1cxgUmq5gNtwSewibalRYnEycticUNl6pj2yEnK2mTg/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">——“渐渐地，我找到了很多帮我更精确地画线条的技巧。”</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4jm7iaq8iaaP6fP7rH9Dzuuu5WHcqvwhwtXxFLGYBlqUWOxS3jribf3khA/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">——“我工作室里的所有工具都带着盲文，而当我需要用色时我会使用色谱。”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4QAuBlIZncwqdgMnrs7GPKe4JcXUzibQ8ax3ctnjQsWAH9e552hC5LOQ/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">——“在我的第一次画展上，我没有让任何人知道我看不见。”</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4kibjYFUt1qyIdfwDlcgFicvfrUlKibFAxhO6YqibROkib29knDV7iaibFnvPw/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">——“我没有告诉别人真相，不是因为我觉得害羞难堪，只是我不希望影响大家对这幅画本身的理解和欣赏。”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">John Bramblitt让更多人关注到盲人这个群体，也对绘画有了新的定义。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4kyKXGOKY6AjwMB07WibdIibY0OlkQRDDrJQM0PxkasCC1sxcsblH6ziag/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">有些人不是生来伟大，但却拥有伟大的品质。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:auto !important;height:auto !important;\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71VLcxFbqoibQeWicUyWeAibVS4icHPYUoTAmpzCVLw4mJsMNibiamtdG2jqcWVEq1wmKEnZCyUllAQiclV0w/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427926541', '', '0', 'http://', '', '86986', '0', '4659');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`, `click_count`, `rel_clickcount`, `love` ) VALUES  ('142', '19', '中国10大处女古镇，别再只去丽江凤凰啦', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#99bb00;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><strong><span><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/NPv8Ib9HvuIYJ7ygEhEAhRpcRQlxsEMlo9k5M7JWepianJicv22GaBDyBUHNwWoV1IPWibfiboZvAXCl9qC2bkIRiaA/0\" width=\"300\" height=\"36\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	 提醒:点击标题下方的“</span><span><span style=\"color:#0070c0;\">实实商城</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">”即可免费订阅我，随时发现，采集，分享你喜欢的一切。</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></strong></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></strong></span></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#99bb00;font-size:18px;\"><strong>这个春天</strong></span><span style=\"color:#99bb00;font-size:18px;\"><strong>，去什么地方玩又让你头疼了吧？不要只知道去平遥、婺源、丽江、凤凰了，游客多得让人几乎喘不上气来，哪儿还叫旅游啊。快来看看最能让你清净的古镇吧！</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;margin:0px 0px 45px;color:#333333;\" class=\"m-box\">\r\n	<h2 style=\"color:#121212;font-size:26px;font-weight:normal;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>1.侨乡和顺：绝胜小苏杭的边陲魅力名镇</strong></span> \r\n	</h2>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"f-pr\">\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/cdc1bbf8-d52d-4a11-b62f-76264c649eaa.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"193\" /> \r\n		<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-share-img\">\r\n			<div style=\"text-align:left !important;margin:0px;font-size:12px;\" id=\"bdshare\" class=\"bdshare_t bds_tools get-codes-bdshare\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:justify;color:#ffffff;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#9933e5;\">和顺，云南最大的侨乡，至今仍较完整地保留着滇西一带明、清时代的建筑风貌。</span><span style=\"color:#9933e5;\">顺，</span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:justify;color:#ffffff;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#9933e5;\">走进和顺，就像走进了一座文化迷宫。成千幢特色民居依山傍水，鳞次栉比，伸手便可触摸到斑驳的岁月和丰厚的文化。</span>云南最大的侨乡，至今仍较完整地保留着滇西一带明、清时代的建筑风</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:16px;\"><strong>2.査济：黄山脚下最后的处女古村</strong></span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/e6353edc-4a78-4858-93d1-b88fb3507843.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"190\" /> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\">同样是小桥流水人家，江南的那些则已被众多的客人蹂躏踩踏，查济仍然如村姑处子。</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\">它的规模之大，在皖南堪称第一，也是中国现存最大的古民居群之一。现在村里还保存着唯一的元代建筑——德公厅屋，还有最完整的明代建筑——爱月堂、二甲祠，众多的明清代建筑保护较完整。</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\">它破败颓废的沧桑之美，能让人看见中国乡村时代辉煌的历史。</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:16px;\"><strong>3.湖南隐秘古城黔阳：比凤凰繁荣早千年</strong></span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/861a2559-c515-422e-a694-1aa470d1b419.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"161\" /> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\">除了凤凰，湘西还有许多不被外人知的隐秘古城，黔阳古城便是其中之一。</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\">它是全国保存最为完好的明清古城之一，三面环水，是湘楚苗地边陲重镇，素有“滇黔门户”和“湘西第一古镇”之称。</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\">比云南丽江大研古镇早1400年，较湖南省内的凤凰古城早将近千年。</span><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>4.丙安古镇：赤水河畔“老照片”</strong></span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/3e2e3e77-3566-4994-9ab8-6b5f36df9e13.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"170\" />&nbsp;</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">丙安古镇位于赤水河畔，明清时期是川南入黔古道的重要场镇。</span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">这里交通不便，使得千年古镇丙安保持了独特风韵——这里除新修的一座悬索吊桥外，至今只有一条水路可到城堡脚下，隔河望去，整个古镇基本保持了明清以来赤水河谷的古城堡原貌。</span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">沿着带有青苔的石板街走下去，眼看着斑驳的木板墙、老建筑，好似走进了遥远的明朝清代和民国时期。</span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>5.福建漳州赵家堡：南宋皇族后裔悲情遗梦</strong></span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/4ff3f3bc-6c49-4728-9135-e31e3701ce86.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"216\" />&nbsp;</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">地处福建漳州的赵家堡是宋代赵氏皇族后裔于明朝万历年间，仿照北宋故都汴京城的立意布局建造而成的。</span></span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">绵延四百年至今仍保留着相当完整的原型风貌，素有“宋城”、“闽南小汴京”之称。</span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">有人说这是一座没有皇帝的皇城，更是一个无法“完璧”的遗梦。</span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>6.宝山石头城：最后的纳西族乐土</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/65159ee0-e4be-49d7-b935-beb71958a1d0.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"216\" />&nbsp;</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">丽江除了闻名遐迩的大研古城外，在距丽江以北约120公里的金沙江大峡谷旁，还有一座古城，因其建在一块庞大独立的蘑菇状岩石上，故称石头城。</span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">这里是纳西人最原始的聚集地。无论是房屋、建筑，抑或语言，都很好地保留了纳西族群最真实的一面。</span> </span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>7.茶马古道重镇寺登街：千年集市无人打扰</strong></span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><img style=\"width:284px;height:205px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/abcf34cf-1763-4b1b-9f38-b594e262c745.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"247\" />&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;\">我们已没有机会去十年前的大理和丽江，但可以去看看现在的寺登街。</span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;\">这个曾经的茶马古道上的重镇，依旧保持着千年古集市的旧有风貌，尚未被过多游人打扰，堪称茶马古道上唯一幸存的集市。</span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"></span></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>8.江西铅山：养在深闺人未识的千年古镇</strong></span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/be157f38-51bc-44ad-9bb6-3a485c6aa416.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"216\" />&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;\">说起江西的古镇，估计全国人民的第一反应都是婺源。其实，婺源只是个村庄，并不能称得上古镇。</span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;\">在漫长的历史长河中，江西确曾涌现过数个著名城镇，她们是水运时代市井繁华的代表，也大多在商品经济的洪流中迅速衰落不为外人熟知。曾有“八省通衢”之称的铅山便是其中之一。</span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"></span></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>9.广西大圩古镇：连个公厕都难找</strong></span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/58c2e05d-824b-48fb-8ce7-5de30dc168a1.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"216\" />&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">“圩”在南方指集市，“大圩”顾名思义就是很大的集市。</span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">不过大圩也确实名不虚传，是一座有千年历史的古镇，古镇始于北宋，兴于明清，鼎盛于民国，成为当年广西四大圩镇之首。</span> </span></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9933e5;\"> \r\n		<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;margin:0px 0px 45px;color:#333333;\" class=\"m-box\">\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n				<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\">如今这里商业痕迹却很少，少到连公厕都很难。</span> </span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n				<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:16px;\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n				<span style=\"color:#9933e5;font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:16px;\">10.偏岩古镇：夫妻树下探秘另类女铁匠</span></strong> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px;\" class=\"m-comments\">\r\n				<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;margin:0px;color:#333333;\" class=\"f-pr\">\r\n					<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://u2.zhenyouliao.com/images/20140213/905c36af-97f8-489f-9d31-fc9f57395776.jpg\" width=\"288\" height=\"194\" />&nbsp;\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;margin:0px;color:#333333;\" class=\"f-pr\">\r\n					<span style=\"color:#9933e5;\">偏岩古镇是重庆通往华莹古道上的一座工商古镇，昔日商贾云集，历300余年，保存较完好，街两边的房屋建筑没有进行过任何的翻修，仍保持着原有的古朴风貌。</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:justify;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;color:#333333;\">\r\n					<span style=\"color:#9933e5;\">除了小桥、流水，老街、古屋，镇上最吸引人的当属这里的“鸳鸯桥”、“夫妻树”和女铁匠。</span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n</span>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff