i\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">内心强大到混蛋，</span> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\">比什么都重要。</span> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3e3e3e;font-size:15px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617306\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9WjxCgOuq3hUpMC6cWPqA2Z2f9JupTVsV6rUNLEQpkhq9MOlcZgIm96pg/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /></span></span></strong> </strong>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:inherit;\">当归红枣羊肉汤</span> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:inherit;\">食材：羊肉500g、当归20g、红枣20g、桂圆肉10g、枸杞10g、姜适量</span> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:inherit;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">1)把所有材料准备好；2)羊排洗干净，切成块；3)放入煮开的水中焯一下，撇去浮沫，<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">取出备用；</span>4)姜去皮，红枣去核，当归、桂圆肉、枸杞用水泡洗干净；</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">5)把所有处理好的材料放进汤锅中，注入适量清水，大火煮开转中小火煮1.5—2小时即可。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617307\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9WjaUafPibyMtCOmtH1r9ZqAvqfGe2QkdWM1ia6K4wwowXzVGgkYDhcyF1g/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /></span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">懒人大酱汤</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	食材：蘑菇、金针菇、牛肉片、韩式大酱、豆腐\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">1)豆腐切块；蘑菇和金针菇洗净沥干；2)牛肉片在沸水中快速焯一下后取出；3)锅中注入清水，放入大酱，中小火将大酱融化，其间不断搅拌。水开后放入豆腐，小火煮5分钟；4)放入蘑菇继续小火煮一会儿；</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">5)最后倒入牛肉片和金针菇，大火煮开后立即关火。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617308\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9WjSYKWyNgriahCasibKNURMRPOiakRlVyibarr3N6lmtpYia7BK95TcorlUgw/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">黄芪乌鸡汤食材：乌鸡1只、黄芪适量、大枣适量、枸杞适量、葱适量、姜适量、盐适量、花雕酒适量</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<strong> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">1)乌鸡洗净；</span><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">2)配料准备好；</span><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">3)将砂锅内注满水，将乌鸡放入其中。烧开，撇去浮沫；</span><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">4)将黄芪片放入；</span><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">5)放入葱姜；</span><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">6)放入大枣；</span><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">7)倒入少许料酒；</span><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">8)小火慢炖一小时左右，放入枸杞；</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</strong> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">9)再炖十分钟左右，加入少许盐调味，即可关火。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617309\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9WjpScs2liaWth11PnOojIcHNtoozx45d1c0p0uZv3NJL5WSroEufOxplA/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">玉米板栗排骨汤食材：排骨500g、甜玉米1根、栗子肉10粒、胡萝卜40g、葱姜适量、大料3个、黄酒20ml、盐适量、胡椒粉适量</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">1)准备好所有的食材；2)排骨洗净冷水入锅焯烫过凉；3)甜玉米洗净切段，胡萝卜切块，栗子清水浸泡片刻；4)汤煲中加入热水加入葱姜、黄酒，<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">再放入大料。</span>5)加入排骨，<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">加盖大火煮开小火炖煮20分钟；</span>6)然后加入玉米，栗子继续小火炖煮30分钟；7)再加入胡萝卜炖煮10分钟；8)加入盐，<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">加入胡椒粉调味；</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">9)大火煮开关火。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617310\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9Wj6TqHGkJEmv1wdo4ApzlPicgk69qT54H2NaBaVJ9tELNARtE5eib86Stg/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">番茄鱼丸豆腐汤食材：番茄240g、鱼丸150g、豆腐150g、泡发木耳50g、油适量、盐适量、小葱1颗、蒜3瓣</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">1)准备材料；2)豆腐切方块，木耳随意切几刀，番茄切小块，葱蒜切碎，鱼丸切成小块。3)汤锅里倒适量的油。4)先下葱蒜，跟紧就下番茄；5)番茄炒变色，下木耳；6)木耳炒倒下鱼丸；7)翻炒均加盐调味；8)加入适量的开水；<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">待煮开下豆腐；</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\">9)等到锅开，调入芡粉；</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\">10)再沸腾就可盛起，散点葱花即可。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617311\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9WjrNicayYVzoib31WheibGSwWHmwlSWVk5ia8xvyu6kyGziabps1ryia7ZK3Fg/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">鲜奶虾海参汤食材：冻干海刺参3个、虾干20g、干香菇10g、海珍汤10g、牛奶250g、蔬之鲜适量、盐适量</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">1)准备材料；2)将海参泡12小时，<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">将香菇泡半天；</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">3)适量的清水煮开</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">，放虾干；</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\">4)放浸泡好的香菇；</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\">5)汤煮开后，放入海珍汤；</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\">6)煮开后，放入牛奶，放发好的海参；</span></span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\">7)适量的盐，适量的蔬之鲜。煮开就可以起锅了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617312\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9Wjg6s0oLBIqHOKya6MTw6o4ZAlKyZA2biaQ0q0z0a0UvVyUBaDicuHKR7w/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">白萝卜海带排骨汤食材：排骨1500g、白萝卜300g、干海带50g、油适量、盐适量、小葱适量、姜适量</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">1)将排骨斩成小块，冲洗干净；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">2)煮上一锅开水焯烫排骨；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">3)倒掉焯烫排骨的污水，洗净排骨，换上一锅清水，将排骨还有葱段和姜块投入锅中；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">4)大火煮开，小火炖煮1小时即可得到一锅原味排骨浓汤；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">5)将干海带泡开，<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">随意切成小块；</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\">6)白萝卜切片；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">7)锅里倒少量的油，先下葱炸锅，</span><span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;font-size:1em;\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">再下萝卜和海带；</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\">8)炒均加盐调味；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\">9)舀几勺原味排骨浓汤入锅；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;font-family:inherit;color:#7f7f7f;font-size:1em;\">10)盖锅，将萝卜煮熟就好了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img style=\"width:327px !important;height:auto !important;\" id=\"c1426672617313\" class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/sfBGoOHy71WegqkdEgrG6oB1hs9Ak9Wjolo9SWrT0rzwxIFIkHm7VIibOiaM08nQUocu8vZKqE3949JiazDXlgyFw/0?tp=webp&wxfrom=5\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">黑木耳红枣汤食材：黑木耳150g、红枣60g、清水600ml</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">做法：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">1)将木耳提前两小时泡软；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">2)红枣也浸在水中十几分钟，方便清洗褶皱处的灰尘；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">3)将木耳和红枣清洗干净，放入锅内，注入适量的清水；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">4)大火煮开；</span></span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">5)转小火炖至汤汁粘稠，大约30分钟；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7f7f7f;\">6)盛到一个的小沙锅里就可以享用了。一般是不用加糖，红枣是很甜的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"></span></span></strong>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1427927620', '', '0', 'http://', '', '98960', '0', '774');
